- backend/app/config.py — all settings from env (OPENAI_API_KEY, OPENAI_BASE_URL optional, CHROMA_PERSIST_DIR, KNOWLEDGE_DIR, models, retrieve_top_k, adaptive_rag_enabled, rag_hyde_enabled, retrieve_max_distance, Jira/Bitbucket/Confluence/Google optional vars)
